{"type":"message","id":"02e5fb84","parentId":"ab2364b1","timestamp":"2026-04-01T09:58:36.687Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session is the cron job itself. Let me check if this cron job has any user message in the last 5 minutes. The updatedAt is 1775037499760 which is the last message from the cron job, not a user message. Let me check if there's any actual user interaction.\n\nActually, looking at the sessions_list result, the only session is the cron job itself with no user messages. This means there's no active conversation with a user. I should proceed with the autonomous learning task.\n\nWait, but the session's last message is from the cron job (role: assistant with toolCall). There's no user message in this session. \n\nSince this cron run is the only session and it doesn't contain any user messages, there's no active conversation to interact with, so I should move forward with the learning task. Let me also do a broader search to see if there are any other recent sessions I might have missed.","thinkingSignature":"6d2723900651d4fd1dfb06d2b4a0cb14a13b58b20e7bfe95dafde6c87f5ec977"},{"type":"text","text":"没有其他活跃会话，只有当前这个cron任务自身在运行。继续执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pajwgd3pcg7z_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":828,"output":251,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45060,"cost":{"input":0.00024839999999999997,"output":0.0003012,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0018690299999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775037509524}}
